    -- dark blade (invisible), handle ring (violet, mesh 3270017) with
    -- dark Fire (purple), 8 ring spikes around the handle.
    -- 4 modes: Neutral, Fire (fireboost +5), Ice, Dark.
    -- Abilities:
    --   1) Combo1a/1b/1c — 3-hit combo, last hit is a dark laser beam.
    --   2) BlizzardSword — ice spikes that home on nearby enemies.
    --   3) FlameTrail — leaves fire trails that damage on touch.
    --   4) LifeDrain — pulls nearest enemy, drains HP, heals self.
    --   5) FireMode — transforms, gains flame wings, fire AoE shockwave.
    -- Damage: 15-25 normal, 25-45 crit, crtrate 12.
