    -- SPIKEBALL NOOB ─────────────────────────────────────────
    -- Adapted from the Spike suit script.
    -- Lime green BlockMesh suit parts (Torso/Arms/Legs/Head) that are 5x larger.
    -- MP resource system (1250000 max, regenerates +4.5/charge tick).
    -- Abilities (cost MP):
    --   1) summonSpikes — 18 torso + 2x2 arm/leg spikes (mesh 1033714), animated growth.
    --   2) sideSlash — spike melee swing, 5-10 dmg + trail.
    --   3) spikeShoot — continuous spike projectiles, 10-24 dmg each (costs 6 MP/shot).
    --   4) flip — backflip + shoot 6 spikes, 30 MP.
    --   5) spinSlash — dual spike spin, 360°5 rotation, 2-5 dmg, 150 MP.
    --   6) spikeWall — 13 spikes in a wall, 2-12 AoE dmg, 60 MP.
    --   7) spikeCannon — random direction spike spray, 8 MP/shot.
    --   8) spikeRoll — 30 body spikes + spin, 600 MP.
    -- Spike projectile: raycast-stepped, sticks into targets, 10-24 dmg.
    -- Health 250. WalkSpeed 18.
    elseif characterType == "spikeball_noob" then
        h.WalkSpeed = 18
        h.MaxHealth = 250; h.Health = 250
        colorModel(model, Color3.fromRGB(50, 255, 50))
        local rArm = model:FindFirstChild("Right Arm")
