    -- MAD CARD NOOB ───────────────────────────────────────────
    -- Adapted from Shackluster's Mad Card script.
    -- Holds a mailbox weapon (Tawny handle + Stone grey front plate
    -- with decal 140490792, black opening slot).
    -- Music 596220347 looped (vol 0.6), Final Inbox music 195916147 (vol 3).
