    --   2) papercutChaos — forward mails that spawn spiraling side mails.
    --   3) mailboxMadness — 15 random-position spiral sprays.
    --   4) finalInbox — ultimate multi-direction mail storm, 50-125 speed.
    --   5) cardMadness — ultimate combo (all abilities chained).
    -- Each mail: 15-45 dmg on touch, BodyVelocity projectile.
    -- Chuck sound 11900833 (pitch 2) per mail.
    -- HP = math.huge, WalkSpeed 16.
